information: The company LA VEGA DE CIEZA, SCA, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1993, which operates in the Fruit industry. It also operates in the Apricot industries. It is based in Cieza, Spain.
products: Fruta de hueso y kaki | Nectarina | Paraguayo | Albaricoque | Melocoton | Platerina | Kaki | Ciruela
